{"tid":1815423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家唔記得半年前和你塞點樣應對捉鬼問題","createTime":"2020-01-07T13:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T03:51:26.000Z","uid":76310,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc229161d2dfc837866f721ffed0f652fa011b6","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"和你塞機場，大家唔記得晒？<br />\n大家記性好差<br />\n捉鬼呢個老問題，其實半年前已經講<br />\n而家衰過半年前<br />\n<br />\n果時大家都認為，唔捉鬼，咪好似信用卡任你碌<br />\n捉又驚捉錯，因為單憑外表睇唔出係唔係鬼<br />\n話乜野剷青，大大隻隻就係鬼<br />\n或者話乜野有耳機，大大隻就係鬼<br />\n話你聽，有d個樣學生哥咁，仲要好鬼瘦，係鬼黎，你見過未<br />\n有d大媽大叔都係鬼，睇樣完全睇唔出<br />\n<br />\n但當時大家捉左付国豪出黎<br />\n半年者，咁快唔記得？<br />\n<br />\n講個重點係乜<br />\n立軍令狀：<br />\n大家大概同意有原則乜唔可以做，一做就算真自己友，一律當鬼計<br />\n同樣地，就算真既鬼做左可以接受既野，一律當手足計<br />\n<br />\n以剛剛維園遊行來計，有手足攪到大隊行唔到<br />\n以行為來考慮，不是以外表或衣著來考慮，大家接唔接到先<br />\n接受到，手足<br />\n接受唔到，鬼"},{"pid":"e98c5ca3f664810cbf7d3e7c6d0fd7a47556e6d4","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"你班人真係好無記性<br />\n記住當日以行為來界定鬼定手足<br />\n可接受行為，鬼做都當手足計<br />\n不可接受行為，手足當鬼計"},{"pid":"ed9a7721a425f88ad7bdd08773c36fefb3efd983","tid":1815423,"uid":247493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:21:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n🎉 1.11全城 連儂日 🎉<br />\n        「勇武感謝祭2020」<br />\n<br />\nPart One - 元祖慶典<br />\n時間：14:00 - 17:00<br />\n地點：金鐘元祖連儂牆<br />\n<br />\nPart Two - 遍地連儂 <br />\n時間：19:00 - 22:00<br />\n地點：全港18區<br />\n<br />\n111不分和勇 連儂日見!<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8d3gcvc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8d3gcvc.jpg&h=fe2e9ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X12As3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX12As3y.jpg&h=cd0a735a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06ff1d901e767a5c8b3e81d087235968cf20d28f","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"你班人咁無記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8ff1b1c826868a7bb3edfb85d7cc4972aceab3","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"當日點解捉到付国豪<br />\n仲有個楊乜乜既公安<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地帶頭好激動要衝禁區<br />\n但大家唔衝就私了佢，拎晒佢既證出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁快唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62381259ae8f8e33bdad2a43bfa4d76054010a51","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3e70ede60dfee906af9bb88835627378a7d83f","tid":1815423,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"但講真一句今時對方都用唔同部署<br />\n宜家對面可能有五六十個黑衫便衣係左近<br />\n知道你唔捉鬼佢更加可以派多D<br />\n都要諗辦法拆"},{"pid":"84b55bfcf699660b2dc5a30e429a1345490f75c0","tid":1815423,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXSTZdG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXSTZdG.jpg&h=514103a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4507949659b029750b455438f4277355b27db24f","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"呢個方法可以避免班黑警乜都做<br />\n然後為左不割蓆，死攬出事<br />\n等同比信用卡任刷<br />\n<br />\n當日都係用以行動來判斷<br />\n事前定下方針<br />\n以行動為準"},{"pid":"382c70a75054e7f3ffed550b456af60b110636ec","tid":1815423,"uid":23239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf3d18e68628a0c71f9f9107776d853776a85eb","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"所以遊行時 就算有些人剷青，有耳機，大大隻咁<br />\n出火魔攪獅子銀行<br />\n<br />\n一律以手足計<br />\n<br />\n就算佢真係黑警，幫手對付獅子銀行，一律以手足計算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家明唔明個概念係點"},{"pid":"a22842cd558fbffa6f51220dee49bf6f5699ea8b","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b85340377f7a2c31c7a77d06b0f225210e5979","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31595e4d1a806766498238595617fe1620f53285","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90e88da57665b051151201c410d97994d05ad97","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"關於Donki姐姐朝早講唔好捉鬼嘅故事，獄中嘅戰士有啲嘢想同大家講<br />\n<br />\n有啲長，但係希望大家可以耐心睇哂完佢，同睇埋還押手足封信(圖一)<br />\n========================<br />\n我地係一班孭緊薄既小朋友，曾同四小隊合作過，佢哋既經驗令我地不斷成長，至今捉鬼熱潮，勇武退潮，我不得不出黎發聲。<br />\n<br />\n我地曾經都比人當過係鬼check身分證，學生證，除罩。我地試過企既位置係喺前線防線前面，當時好清晰聽到後排有人嗌前線走呀，佢地係鬼黎㗎，果刻憤怒加失望。<br />\n<br />\n亦都因為被捉鬼比狗跟，咬左半team人，曾經都因為捉鬼撚搞到想退出。<br />\n<br />\n但係我想講既係，場革命唔係為自己，而係為我地既下一代，為我地既未來去抗爭，我記得有個前輩講過一句說話令我好深刻:唔好諗人地可以做d乜，你要諗下，自己可以做d乜。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，就係依句令我明白雖然捉鬼撚令我地好心灰意冷，同時間勇武退潮亦會增大我地風險，但係若然退出就更加對唔住義士，手足。<br />\n<br />\n我相信黎緊d狗一定會繼續派人捉鬼分化我地，只要我地唔捉鬼就唔會中招，現場再有人捉鬼大家就大大力屌捉鬼既人係分化撚。<br />\n<br />\n要走既，就唔好在諗唔開心既嘢喇，感激你地半年並肩作戰，要繼續留既，調整好心態，繼續抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n同時我在此向香港人承諾，就算本小隊得返我一個都會繼續抗爭，因為fight for freedom,stand with hongkong.<br />\n<br />\n附上一封小隊還押手足既信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以呢個例子為例<br />\n前線無做任何野違反底線原則，所以一律係手足計"},{"pid":"6f9660d3b431181dc38e70a830e49ca6f82ab61d","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e26c470dca496a1c7d7c4609a8e494bec219b0","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727235c2dafb01282e9cea2b900bcafa4d66433e","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1589d29ab9ab84ffeead0aea1b33a77b7e703fe","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70cf6bb263226b9e9fc96111b6632f429774726","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"以行動為依歸 唔洗捉鬼"},{"pid":"43f067b0ace3b29ff0f865856870e3646792850c","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5872a724330df0e151f2bdf80fca14032ef978b4","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0baccee5dc1c03167bbb24bf8639755d82b93c","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4118c1e2a53c80b73546c05ece83c8af1fef0291","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d2527ee5bf5b88e5ac549dcff85547397f2fb0","tid":1815423,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}